'''锡·史密斯'''（{{lang-en|Theobald Smith}}，{{bd|1859年|7月31日|1934年|12月10日}}，也译作'''西奥博尔德·史密斯'''）是一位美国[[流行病学|流行病学]]家和[[病原学|病原学]]家<ref name="frs">{{Cite journal | last1 = Nuttall | first1 = G. H. F. | author-link = George Nuttall| title = Theobald Smith. 1859-1934 | doi = 10.1098/rsbm.1935.0014 | journal = [[Obituary_Notices_of_Fellows_of_the_Royal_Society|Obituary Notices of Fellows of the Royal Society]] | volume = 1 | issue = 4 | pages = 514–521 | year = 1935 | jstor = 768981| bibcode = 1935SciMo..40..196W }}</ref>，是这一领域的先驱<ref name=Dolman_2003>{{cite book |last1=Dolman |first1=C.E. |last2=Wolfe |first2=R.J. | title = Suppressing the Diseases of Animals and Man: Theobald Smith, Microbiologist | publisher = Boston Medical Library| year = 2003| isbn= 0-674-01220-8}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Middleton |first=James |date=July 1914  |title=A Great American Scientist: Dr. Theobald Smith, Head of The New Department Of Animal Diseases At The Rockefeller Institute |journal=[[World's_Work|The World's Work: A History of Our Time]] |volume=XLIV |issue=2 |pages=299–302 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zegeQtMn9JsC&pg=PA299 |accessdate=2009-08-04 |publisher=Doubleday, Page & Co. }}</ref>，知名于发现了[[過敏性休克|過敏性休克]]中的“锡·史密斯氏现象”（Theobald Smith's phenomenon）<ref name=du>{{cite web|url=http://cornelldu.org/?page=notableDUs|title=1869 - 1930 - Cornell DU Alumni|website=cornelldu.org|accessdate=2018-04-18|archive-date=2018-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180418230612/http://cornelldu.org/?page=notableDUs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

